title: Google Pixel 4 Trouble with Face Unlock
content: I bought Google Pixel 4 and face unlock doesn't work. Previous owner made hard reset and now when i tried to setup Face Unlock, i have trouble "Enrollment was not completed. Certificate expired". One guy said that Android 12 Beta can solve that problem and i updated it) But stil have this problem. What should i do?
